title: Masked thief steals a dozen signed sports jerseys from Saugus barber shop
text:
Masked thief steals a dozen signed sports jerseys from Saugus barber shop 
Published By: Boston.com - Today 
A man broke into Barber Masters in Saugus Wednesday night and took 12 autographed sports jerseys that hung on the walls....
